rComments: Best discussion leader I've had (including high school).  Grading is average.  Tries to get everyone involved with discussion.  Go to office hours and your paper grade will go up by at least one letter grade.  Personal conferences are REALLY helpful.  He knows a lot about writing (maybe too much).  Nerdy and knows it.  Try and you'll do fine.
You will learn how to write better, but grading isn't the easiest. Funny at times, but how funny can you make writing?
